wanted to play like this he should have started the game with 1...e6!} c5 6. a3
({The simple} 6. Bd2 {is also good enough for a slight advantage} Ne7 7. a3
Bxc3 {This is practically forced.} (7... Ba5 8. dxc5 $16 {followed by b2-b4 is
