exf6 {This is Black's more sensible recapture.} 8. Bd3 {Clearing the way for
O-O.} O-O 9. O-O Re8 10. Bf4 {White has more space, better control over the
center, and a 4 vs 3 on the queenside. White can follow up with Re1 and then
