Conclusion: The Caro-Pirc setup with 3...g6 is playable but does not equalize.
White can at the very least count on a slight advantage, usually in the form
of superior central control and more active pieces.}) 8. c3 {Reinforcing the
d4 pawn.} (8. Bh6 $5 {is also rather awkward for Black who can no longer
