[PlyCount "8"]

14... c5 {Super-GM Shakriyar Mamedyarov with the Black pieces has just played .
..c5, attacking White's bishop on b4. What did MVL, with the White pieces,
play?} 15. cxd5 {A strong in-between move, which leaves the knight on e4 en
prise.} exd5 16. Bc3 {Retreating the bishop to safety and unmasking an attack
on the b7 pawn.} O-O 17. Rxb7 Nxc3 18. dxc3 {with this combination, MVL
obtained a decisive advantage and brought the point home in 1-0 Vachier
Lagrave, Maxime (2780)-Mamedyarov, Shakriyar (2772) Wch Rapid Moscow 2019.
This game is annotated in the model games chapter.} *

