[PlyCount "10"]

15... Be7 {Black has just retreated his bishop to e7. What did he miss?} 16.
Bxe6 {A typical sacrifice.} fxe6 17. Qxe6+ Rf7 18. Qxd7 {White recoups the
minor piece and is now two pawns up.} Qxf3 19. Rd3 Qf6 20. Qxb7 {White was two
pawns up and easily won in 1-0 Gazik, Viktor (2502)-Villegas, Pierre (2364)
Titled Tuesday 2020.} *

