9... h6 {Black wanted to get rid of the knight on g5 and so played ...h6. What
did he miss?} 10. Qd8+ {A beautiful queen 'sacrifice'.} Kxd8 11. Nxf7+ Kc7 12.
Nxe5 {Black's pawn structure is ruined and his king was forced to c7. White
followed up with Bf4 and O-O-O and quickly won in 1-0 Brooks, Michael (2430)
-Ulrich, Tommy (2206) Saint Louis 2012.} *

