18... Qa5 {IM Miguoel Admiraal has just developed his queen to a5. How did GM
Nils Grandelius with the White pieces punish this queen sortie?} 19. Ne5 {
A very strong move, attacking the rook on d7 and the bishop on g4. As GM John
Nunn famously said, loose pieces drop off!} Bxe5 20. Bxg4 {Picking up the
bishop and renewing the attack on the rook on d7.} Rxd4 21. Bxh5 Rxd2 22. Bxd2
Qxd2 23. Rxe5 gxh5 24. Qxb7 {White got a decisive advantage with this
combination. Black's pawn structure is in tatter and his king is too exposed.
In fact, Black immediately resigned in 1-0 Grandelius, Nils (2681)-Admiraal,
Miguoel (2510) 2019.} *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
